California Orange

R(price) R720.00

Hybrid – 50% Sativa / 50% Indica THC: 15%

Effects: Energizing, Euphoria, Focus, Happy, Relaxing
Flavors: Citrus, Fruity, Orange, Sweet, Tropical
Aromas: Earthy, Fruity, Orange, Sweet

California Orange, also known by C.O.B. or California Orange Bud, is a balanced Indica-Sativa mix. California Orange was created in the 1980s, before online growers could discuss and trademark their strain genetics. It has an undetermined parentage. Its fresh citrus aroma is undeniable. This strain has a high THC content of 10 to 15%. However, it is well-known for its potent mental high.

Effects: Body High
Flavors: Berry, Fruity, Lemon

Eve was right to think so, if she were reaching out for the Forbidden Fruit. We know apples are delicious, but this strain will make you forget about everything else. This hybrid, 70/30, is a cross between two very flavorful, effects-heavy strains Cherry Pie and Tangie to produce a delicious, nighttime bud.

item.content:encoded:
Sour Diesel

R(price) R720.00

Sativa Dominant Hybrid – 90% Sativa / 10% Indica THC: 26%, CBD: 2%, CBN: 4%

Effects: Creative, Energizing, Euphoria, Happy, Uplifting
Flavors: Candy, Citrus, Dank, Diesel, Skunky, Sweet
Aromas: Dank, Diesel, Sweet

Sour Diesel is a great strain that will make you have a blast. It’s also a smash-in the-face of Chemdawgand another Sativa we are still trying to identify. It is not known who it was originally bred. Most people refer to him/her as “A.J.” and “Asshole Joe”. Although they don’t affect the base effects of Sour Diesel’s CBD and 4% CBN, these chemical compounds provide a different intensity than you can control. Sour Diesel, also known as “Sour Deez” or “Sour D”, brings an almost pure 90% Sativa effect to your mind. You will not be able to resist.

item.content:encoded:
Slurricane

R(price) R720.00

Indica Dominant Hybrid – 60% Indica / 40% Sativa THC: 20% – 28%

Effects: Body High, Cerebral, Hungry, Tingly, Uplifting
Flavors: Berry, Fruity, Herbal, Spicy, Sweet, Tropical
Aromas: Berry, Earthy, Pungent, Spicy, Sweet, Tropical

Slurricane quickly grew to be one of the most popular strains in the cannabis market. It is now considered one of the best indica strains. In House Genetics is a legend thanks to their cross of Do-Si Dos and Purple Punch. The team has experimented with many phenotypes, and it looks like we may see Slurricane cross with other strains to make some truly amazing plants.
